embeddedItem.name: Enigmatic Ectostella
embeddedItem.desc: A fathomless crystal. Ascension material for the Trailblazer.
embeddedItem.lore:
Severed from the highest of beings, this crystal reflects ever-changing mirages. The past and future intertwine on each of its countless facets, attempting to swallow up all observers.

"Civilization is but a thin sheet of ice on top of the deep dark ocean of chaos."

175713.name: Trailblazer
175713.lore:
A girl/boy who boarded the Astral Express.
They chose to travel with the Astral Express to eliminate the dangers posed by the Stellaron.
